NAME: DU
DESCRIPTION: DAIT user oversees specific grants/contract that use ImmPort.  He/she will notifies the DAIT BISC PO when new research grants/contracts are awarded

NAME: PO
DESCRIPTION: DAIT BISC Project Officer oversees the BISC II project.  He/she performs system access control functions and/or delegates them to other DAIT employess for a Functional Administrator.
